charges.charge_disposition: The Defendant, Brian Pizetsky, pled guilty to the 1 Count Information. Defendant must pay a $100 Special Assessment. Defendant to be given credit for time served. The Court recommends defendant receive Drug Treatment while in prison and recommends a facility that provides Drug Treatment such as Fort Dix or Allenwood. (1)
